{"id":357204,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/08/【微盐】身为公民-为他人的不幸而呐喊奔走/","date":"2014-08-07T03:33:28Z","modified":"2014-08-07T03:33:28Z","title":"【微盐】身为公民, 为他人的不幸而呐喊奔走","content":"<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/zd4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-357207\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/zd4.jpg\" alt=\"zd4\" width=\"600\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/zd4.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/zd4-300x275.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/xdd4.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-357211\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/xdd4.jpg\" alt=\"xdd4\" width=\"600\" height=\"527\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/xdd4.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/xdd4-300x263.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/rq41.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-357216\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/rq41.jpg\" alt=\"rq4\" width=\"600\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/rq41.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/08/rq41-300x250.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p>1</p>\n<p><strong>慕容雪村</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>如果你想幸福</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>仅有钱是不够的</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>你需要活在某种文明之中</strong><strong>。</strong><strong>关心自己的生活</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>就必须关心自己的权利</strong>; <strong>如果制度继续做恶</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>你我都将难以幸免</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>身为公民</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>你应该正直</strong><strong>、</strong><strong>勇敢</strong><strong>、</strong><strong>独立而清醒</strong>; <strong>身为公民</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>你应该明白</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>爱国家不等于爱朝廷</strong>; <strong>身为公民</strong>, <strong>为他人的不幸而呐喊奔走</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>是一种高尚的品质</strong><strong>。</strong></p>\n<p><strong> </strong>2</p>\n<p><strong>贪官的妙处</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>他们的胡吃海喝</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>带动了中国酒店业的繁荣昌盛</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>他们的桑拿按摩</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>解决了大量的就业问题</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>他们的</strong>N<strong>套房子</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>促使房产成中国的经济支柱</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>他们的众多</strong>N<strong>奶</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>拉动了中国和世界奢侈品消费的快速增长</strong><strong>；</strong><strong>他们的家人移居国外</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>成功塑造了中国人是世界富人的形象</strong><strong>！</strong><strong>贪官你们辛苦啦</strong><strong>！</strong><strong>你们一个比一个出彩</strong><strong>！</strong></p>\n<p>3</p>\n<p><strong>孙国栋</strong><strong>：</strong><strong>今天是世界人权日</strong><strong>。</strong><strong>人权不是写在纸上的宣言</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>也不是对外作秀的道具</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>而是人所以为人的基本元素</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>是个人自我保护</strong><strong>、</strong><strong>抵御公权侵害的坚实盾牌</strong><strong>。</strong><strong>人权更需要制度的保障</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>否则任何人在任何时候任何地点都可能成为暴政的牺牲品</strong><strong>，</strong><strong>孙志刚</strong><strong>、</strong><strong>刘少奇概莫能外</strong><strong>。</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"color: #404041;\">【微盐】是中国数字时代“<a style=\"color: #336699;\" href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%83%E8%B5%84%E6%96%99\">网络公民话语</a>”系谱整理的<a style=\"color: #336699;\" href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E7%BD%91%E8%AF%AD%E9%9B%86%E9%94%A6\">一个项目</a>，内容选自在中文社交媒体热传，亦遭到审查者删除的时政评论帖。</p>\n<p style=\"color: #404041;\"><a style=\"color: #336699;\" href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/cdtimes./index.html?u=chinese\">中国数字时代亚马逊镜像</a>（墙内可直接点击）</p>\n","author":1023,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[22111,9050,8994,25019,9371]}